00:17:15,650 --> 00:17:19,750
admit an entire different set of
people who would probably never

321
00:17:19,750 --> 00:17:23,890
have made it to MIT,
and they would do great.

322
00:17:23,890 --> 00:17:28,580
So this was really the
core of the gamble.

