341
00:18:35,540 --> 00:18:39,910
why they want to come, what
people write about them,

342
00:18:39,910 --> 00:18:41,120
what are their experiences.

343
00:18:41,120 --> 00:18:43,120
But that way, we don't
need to worry so much

344
00:18:43,120 --> 00:18:45,900
about trying to understand what
their grades might be or might

345
00:18:45,900 --> 00:18:46,400
mean.

346
00:18:46,400 --> 00:18:49,430
Or you don't need to
have gone to college.

